明日は週末　おやすみなさいだよ
Tomorrow is the weekend, it's 'good night'

59
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:54,200
家飲み！
Drinking at home!

60
00:03:54,200 --> 00:03:55,300
最高！
The best!

61
